<h1> Welcome to Craps! </h1>

<h3> The rules of the game </h3>
<ul>
	<li><p>Roll to start </p></li>
	<li><p>If first roll is 7 or 11, you win</p></li>
	<li><p>If first roll is 2, 3, or 12, you lose</p></li>
	<li><p>Otherwise, the roll becomes your target. Roll again until you roll the target, and you win. If you roll a 7, you lose.</p></li>
</ul>

